TextEng: Sorry, I didn't mean to interrupt.
Me sorry. Me not mean to interrupt.
I think I'll be going now.
What's your problem? I'm just trying to be friendly.
Text: 뭐가 문제야? 그냥 친하게 지내려는 건데.

TextEng: Me go now.
Why you so mad? Me just want be talk at you.
Text: 왜 그렇게 화나? 나 그냥 말하고 싶었어.

TextEng: Why do you want to meet Lady Aribeth so badly?
Text: 왜 아리베스 경을 그렇게 만나고 싶어?

TextEng: How's your training going?
I want to ask you a few questions.
Why you want meet Aribeth so bad?
How you training going?
Me want ask you some questions.
What can you tell me about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭘 알려줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Have you heard those rumors about a cure for the plague?
How do you like training here at the Academy?
What you know 'bout plague?
You hear stuff 'bout cure for plague?
You like training at Academy?
I won't take much of your time. I promise.
Text: 시간 많이 안 걸릴 거야. 약속해.

TextEng: Me speak at you quick. Me promise me not use much time.
Text: 나 빨리 말할게. 나 시간 많이 안 걸려. 약속해.

TextEng: You better answer my questions if you know what's good for you!
Text: 다치기 싫으면 내 질문에 답하는 게 좋을 거야!

TextEng: You answer me question or you be sorry!
Text: 나 질문 답해, 안 그러면 나중에 후회해!
